OL,3,CAssisted dying would be 'wrong',
OL,4,CArchbishop of Westminster tells ITV
OL,5,CNews
OL,7,FThe Head of the Catholic Church speaks
OL,8,Fto ITV News' Paul Brand about why he
OL,9,Fis urging Catholics to write to their
OL,10,FMPs and oppose the move
OL,12,FWords by Georgia Ziebart, ITV News
OL,13,FProducer
OL,15,FThe Head of the Catholic Church in
OL,16,FEngland and Wales has told ITV News
OL,17,Fthat people would be wrong to seek an
OL,18,Fassisted death if the law is changed.
