OL,3,CAssisted dying would be 'wrong',
OL,4,CArchbishop of Westminster tells ITV
OL,5,CNews
OL,7,FIn an exclusive interview with ITV
OL,8,FNews' UK Editor Paul Brand, Archbishop
OL,9,Fof Westminster Cardinal Vincent
OL,10,FNichols said assisted dying would
OL,11,F"shift the foundations" of society.
OL,13,FHe was speaking as MPs prepare to
OL,14,Fdebate a bill next month which would
OL,15,Fallow people a terminally ill patient
OL,16,Fto choose to end their life.
OL,18,FAssisted dying is already legal in
OL,19,Fother countries such as Switzerland,
OL,20,Fthe Netherlands, Canada and certain US
OL,21,Fstates.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
