OL,3,CAssisted dying would be 'wrong',
OL,4,CArchbishop of Westminster tells ITV
OL,5,CNews
OL,7,FBut Cardinal Nichols said the way
OL,8,Flegislation has been used in such
OL,9,Fcountries should serve as a warning.
OL,11,F"The experience of most countries
OL,12,Fwhere this has been introduced, the
OL,13,Fcircumstances are widened and
OL,14,Fwidened," the Archbishop said.
OL,16,FThe Archbishop also urged Catholics to
OL,17,Fconsider the consequences of this law
OL,18,Fchange on the vulnerable in society.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
