OL,3,CAssisted dying would be 'wrong',
OL,4,CArchbishop of Westminster tells ITV
OL,5,CNews
OL,7,F"I think it brings such fear to people
OL,8,Fwho might feel vulnerable that sooner
OL,9,For later they will be expected to take
OL,10,Fthis step. The right to die can
OL,11,Fquickly become a duty to die."
OL,13,FAsked whether he thought it would be
OL,14,Fsinful for somebody to seek an
OL,15,Fassisted death, the Archbishop
OL,16,Fanswered that for somebody who is
OL,17,F"very clear in their mind", he would
OL,18,F"ask them to think again."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
