OL,3,CAssisted dying would be 'wrong',
OL,4,CArchbishop of Westminster tells ITV
OL,5,CNews
OL,7,F"If they ask me, I would say, I think
OL,8,Fyou're wrong," the Archbishop said, "I
OL,9,Fthink it's taking a freedom to
OL,10,Fyourself that you don't possess."
OL,12,F"My life is not my own possession," he
OL,13,Fadded, "I believe it's a gift from our
OL,14,Fcreator, and it should end in that
OL,15,Fsame way: as being called, rather than
OL,16,Fdeciding I'm going to walk out."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
