OL,3,CAssisted dying would be 'wrong',
OL,4,CArchbishop of Westminster tells ITV
OL,5,CNews
OL,7,FShown the video, the Archbishop
OL,8,Femphasised that he did not wish Helen
OL,9,Fto suffer, and that he hoped there
OL,10,Fwould be ways to help manage her pain.
OL,12,F"But on the other hand," he said, "I
OL,13,Fhave to say, this is what you're
OL,14,Fgiven."
OL,16,F"I don't know many people whose lives
OL,17,Fhave included no suffering," he said.
OL,18,F"Suffering is a necessary part of
OL,19,Fbeing human, of being God's creation."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
