OL,3,CAssisted dying would be 'wrong',
OL,4,CArchbishop of Westminster tells ITV
OL,5,CNews
OL,7,FCardinal Nichols' comments come as a
OL,8,Fpoll showed two-thirds of people in
OL,9,FEngland and Wales would support
OL,10,Fassisted dying being legalised for
OL,11,Fterminally ill adults.
OL,13,FBut the Archbishop urged people of
OL,14,Ffaith not to be forgetful of God when
OL,15,Fmaking decisions.
OL,17,F"When we forget God, then we end up
OL,18,Fbelittling the human person. They
OL,19,Fbecome disposable, they subject maybe
OL,20,Fto somebody else's will," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
