OL,3,CAssisted dying would be 'wrong',
OL,4,CArchbishop of Westminster tells ITV
OL,5,CNews
OL,7,FHe told Catholics not to shy away from
OL,8,Fdebate, to write to MPs and express
OL,9,Ftheir views before the vote.
OL,11,F"I think it's important that MPs hear
OL,12,Fnot just the headlines of campaigning
OL,13,Fgroups, but the heartfelt concerns,
OL,14,Ffears and beliefs of people whom they
OL,15,Frepresent."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
