OL,3,CAssisted dying would be 'wrong',
OL,4,CArchbishop of Westminster tells ITV
OL,5,CNews
OL,7,FIn March, ITV News filmed the now
OL,8,FPrime Minister, Sir Keir Starmer,
OL,9,Ftelling assisted dying campaigner
OL,10,FEsther Rantzen that he wanted a debate
OL,11,Fand vote on the matter within the
OL,12,Fcurrent parliament.
OL,14,FThe Labour leader is personally in
OL,15,Ffavour of assisted dying but has said
OL,16,Fhe would allow his MPs to have a free
OL,17,Fvote on the matter, meaning they can
OL,18,Fmake their own mind up about whether
OL,19,Fto support the bill or not.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
