OL,3,CAssisted dying would be 'wrong',
OL,4,CArchbishop of Westminster tells ITV
OL,5,CNews
OL,7,FAsked whether he was worried that
OL,8,Fassisted dying would be legalised in
OL,9,FBritain, the Archbishop said he was
OL,10,Fvery worried, and asked Catholics to
OL,11,Fpray about it.
OL,13,F"I do think it would shift the
OL,14,Ffoundations on which we relate to each
OL,15,Fother, on which we look at each other
OL,16,Fat crucial moments in life," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
