OL,3,CAssisted dying would be 'wrong',
OL,4,CArchbishop of Westminster tells ITV
OL,5,CNews
OL,7,F"In those circumstances, a law is a
OL,8,Fgreat deterrent. So a law that permits
OL,9,Fbecomes an encouragement and it will
OL,10,Fencourage people to see each other
OL,11,Fquite differently," he added.
OL,13,F"And that, I think, will undermine the
OL,14,Fgood of our society."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/14
